    <p>Click the <strong>OK</strong> button.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="view_new_grades" data-step-uuid="09F33300-AAE2-0135-15A0-06467EE270FA">
    <h2 id="view_new_grades" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View New Grades</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/002/615/607/original/7095b6ce-0488-416d-a293-7c057ca5be1b.png" srcset="" alt="View New Grades" height="273" width="373">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_09F35BB0-AAE2-0135-15A2-06467EE270FA" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Default grades are automatically entered for all students who do not have a grade. Grades can be changed by clicking the default grade and typing in an updated score.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
